<div class="container">
    <h1>Why Do We Need Frontend?</h1>
    <p>Imagine you want to use a website or an app. Without a frontend, it would be like having a book with all the information inside, but no pictures, colors, or buttons to help you understand or use it.</p>

    <p>The <strong>frontend</strong> makes websites and apps easy and fun to use. It shows you the information in a nice way and lets you click buttons, fill forms, and interact with everything.</p>

    <h2>Why Frontend is Important</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Easy to Use:</strong> Helps people find what they need quickly.</li>
        <li><strong>Interactive:</strong> Lets you click, play, and get instant responses.</li>
        <li><strong>Attractive:</strong> Makes websites look colorful and inviting.</li>
        <li><strong>Works on Any Device:</strong> Makes sure the website looks good on phones, tablets, and computers.</li>
    </ul>

    <p>Every website and app you use has a frontend that helps you understand and enjoy the content.</p>

